{"sn24.15:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 24.15 ","sn24.15:0.2":"1. Sotapattivagga ","sn24.15:0.3":"Hotitathagatosutta ","sn24.15:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn24.15:1.2":"“Kismim nu kho, bhikkhave, sati, kim upadaya, kim abhinivissa evam ditthi uppajjati: ","sn24.15:1.3":"‘hoti tathagato param marana’”ti? ","sn24.15:1.4":"“Bhagavammulaka no, bhante, dhamma …pe… ","sn24.15:1.5":"niyato sambodhiparayano”ti. ","sn24.15:1.6":"Pannarasamam. "}